# Google OAuth client ID for Tardy (project: tardy-app-55642).
#
# This must be an *iOS*-type OAuth client (bundle id com.nikp29.tardy), which is
# a public client with NO client secret and uses PKCE. A Web/Desktop client will
# fail with "client_secret is missing".
#
# The value is a public identifier (it ships in the built app's Info.plist and
# appears in OAuth URLs) — not a secret. It lives here only to keep it out of
# source. Copy this file to `.env` and set the real value; `.env` is gitignored.
GOOGLE_OAUTH_CLIENT_ID=YOUR_IOS_CLIENT_ID.apps.googleusercontent.com
